SQLC <pre><code>ROLLBACK;
</code></pre> <pre><code>xdb_rollback (pConn); // fast
// or
xdb_exec (pConn, "ROLLBACK");
</code></pre> <p>Note</p> <p>Even if there are errors during statement execution, the transaction will not be rolled back automatically. The user must explicitly issue a rollback.</p>
